data.description: Discover the perfect blend of comfort and style in this thoughtfully remodeled 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom manufactured home, nestled on a spacious lot in Spirit Lake, Idaho. With 1080 Square feet of living space and a 2-car garage, this residence features upgrades including updated flooring. Enjoy the convenience of single-level living and a cozy atmosphere, perfect for entertaining and unwinding. Positioned in the heart of Spirit Lake, this charming home offers a serene retreat away from the hustle and bustle, allowing you to truly embrace the tranquility of living in North Idaho.
